title: Falafel King - Lulius Mall
typeOfFood: Fast food, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Lebanese, Turkish, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A fast food chain where vegans could get falafel, hummus, a sharwarma wrap, eggplant & okra stews, and a couple of salads. Vegan dishes are labled "de post" which in Romanian means "religious fasting dish."
